方呎兩房戶，原於4月底首輪銷售以463.5萬元、實呎1.08萬元售出，惟顯示交易未再月有進展，料買家已撻訂，估計遭沒收5%訂金約23萬元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantp/20250509/1746779526775" target="_blank" uhash="684936e0ebbb609942605f411049d987"&gt;https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantp/20250509/1746779526775&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantp/20250509/1746779526775" target="_blank" uhash="684936e0ebbb609942605f411049d987"&gt;https://finance.mingpao.com/fin/instantp/20250509/1746779526775&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31922545&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1742670158681dceee181392_14404980"/><published>2025-05-09T17:26:21+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9918bb9945c15fe736868afd28bdcc69</id><title>連銀行主任都是偷一百萬過大海。你就知大陸搞到香港經濟幾差。不少人都走投無路</title><updated>2025-05-09T17:43:57+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin1778</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-09T17:43:57+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572328947"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572328947"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16211127" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572328947" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250509/20250509_cffa9c620a8a9eea4bb8IqBdt36tljk8.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b42ae0/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250509/20250509_cffa9c620a8a9eea4bb8IqBdt36tljk8.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16211127_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16211127&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;discuss2_1746783693452.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (374.67 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-9 17:43&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31922567&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1742670158681dceee181392_14404980"/><published>2025-05-09T17:43:57+08:00</published></entry></feed>